Deployed Co-op Projects

{/* Project 1 : Rupert */} Rupert: Movie Companion Rupert was created by Orion, Amanda, Ziman, and myself to help find top movies that you might be looking for. Go Ask Rupert

{/* GitHub */}

Personal Projects

Legends : Aria - JavaScript RPG Game This is a passion project of mine where you can play the start of a game that I am currently developing in my off times. It shows a depth of complex job system with 60+ classes programmed. This project is still under development and will be made available for free when I am completed. To run this locally you can download the game and run it with the http-server node module. Source Code
Crystal Clicker: First JavaScript Application This is an onClick based JavaScript game where it gives each crystal a randomly generated whole value, which you then need to meet the target number. Crystal Clicker
